777
01:08:39,141 --> 01:08:44,152
[SPEAKER_08]: 140,000 houses per year that we're building at the moment.

778
01:08:44,172 --> 01:08:47,980
[SPEAKER_08]: 80,000 of those are swallowed up by immigration.

779
01:08:47,960 --> 01:08:48,862
[SPEAKER_08]: Alone!

780
01:08:49,003 --> 01:08:50,406
[SPEAKER_04]: I'm sorry!

781
01:08:50,426 --> 01:08:53,194
[SPEAKER_04]: We are not building enough houses!

782
01:08:53,454 --> 01:08:57,084
[SPEAKER_04]: We are actually going to touch on housing a little later this evening so we're not going to go there.

783
01:08:57,104 --> 01:09:02,679
[SPEAKER_04]: Can I just draw this back to the issue of wages and the cost of living precisely.

784
01:09:02,699 --> 01:09:05,125
[SPEAKER_11]: I want to particularly pay attention

