807
01:11:54,528 --> 01:11:57,491
[SPEAKER_08]: That will save us £50 billion.

808
01:11:58,032 --> 01:12:02,258
[SPEAKER_08]: We would then have an industrial strategy which would promote employment.

809
01:12:02,278 --> 01:12:08,185
[SPEAKER_08]: But let's not forget the opportunities that Brexit will give us once we leave the European Union.

810
01:12:08,225 --> 01:12:11,229
