[SPEAKER_09]: Thank you.

826
01:12:50,342 --> 01:12:51,503
[SPEAKER_09]: Nicholas Sturgeon.

827
01:12:51,483 --> 01:12:55,430
[SPEAKER_09]: the economy means doing more to support business.

828
01:12:55,491 --> 01:13:01,823
[SPEAKER_09]: In Scotland, we are taking 100,000 small businesses out of business rates to try to give them more money to employ people.

829
