840
01:14:06,950 --> 01:14:13,477
[SPEAKER_12]: We can't simply go on growing and growing with more and more production and consumption in a way that creates more pollution that costs more money to clear it up.

841
01:14:13,798 --> 01:14:16,461
[SPEAKER_12]: What we can do is to invest in the greener economy.

