852
01:14:49,536 --> 01:14:52,547
[SPEAKER_12]: Thank you very much indeed Caroline Lucas.

853
01:14:56,628 --> 01:14:57,089
[SPEAKER_04]: Thank you.

854
01:14:57,109 --> 01:14:59,513
[SPEAKER_04]: And that concludes the discussion on the economy.

855
01:14:59,633 --> 01:15:01,115
[SPEAKER_04]: And thank you to Almas for the question.

